{"tid":723430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"識食一定咁食腸仔包","createTime":"2018-06-30T11:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T11:40:18.000Z","uid":66967,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec5e3955c88eab6da97ec92c3fdcfc89533a7f7","tid":723430,"uid":66967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"腸仔包個個都食過 我講嘅係中式麵包包仔成條雞尾腸個種 唔係又加cream又扮pizza又橫切一半扮全條嘅濕9腸仔包<br />\n<br />\n識食一定係慢慢食曬啲麵包先 有時仲會將個麵包mi少少出黎 猜到一舊細細舊 實實地先食 特別有咬口 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食曬成個包先到重點！ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n腸身會痴住少少麵包 個啲麵包碎先正 吸到腸仔嘅咸味 又有個包本身嘅甜味 再配翻全條腸 咬一大節 個種滿足感根本無與倫比<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天竟吃得出那睿智愈來愈記掛<br />\n開始時捱一些苦　栽種絕處的花</span></span><br />\n<br />\n腸仔包根本就應該咁食 簡簡單單一個腸仔包食法 就已足夠睇得出個人嘅性格係點 係米先勞後悅"},{"pid":"c63d68327185b8d6dcbb0a1020b55017e789a07a","tid":723430,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係先食包皮，臨尾先食腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad2db18d943d621c0107be9cb2486746df34fd1","tid":723430,"uid":133333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63d68327185b8d6dcbb0a1020b55017e789a07a","tid":723430,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係先食包皮，臨尾先食腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59eb2770ed354a6b65425e6b4978e8a5534836fe","tid":723430,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad2db18d943d621c0107be9cb2486746df34fd1","tid":723430,"uid":133333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63d68327185b8d6dcbb0a1020b55017e789a07a","tid":723430,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係先食包皮，臨尾先食腸<img src